{
  "title": "hurricaneexposuredata: Data Characterizing Exposure to Hurricanes in United States Counties",
  "upload_type": "software",
  "description": "This repository extends Brooke Anderson and collaborators' original hurricaneexposuredata R package with more recent hurricane exposure data and new PRISM-based rainfall datasets. The package includes county-level distance-, rain-, wind-, and event-based exposure data for Atlantic-basin tropical storms in the United States.",
